snippet.title: WonderSwan - Cho Aniki - Otoko no Tamafuda © 2000 Bandai - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Cho Aniki: Otoko no Tamafuda is a Role-Playing game, developed by C.P. Brain and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 2000.
